{
  "stem": "22803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's when he wrote this Anyways, so later on, when he came out, I guess he held meetings-- Munich was, I guess, the seed bed of this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he held meetings, because I remember our maid coming back from a meeting in the-- in not the pour houses, like in the pubs or so where he-- you know, it was very bad times and he promised better times.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and eventually, Hindenburg, who was president, made him the chancellor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was-- I mean, Hindenburg was an old, senile man already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So then when he had power-- but then he lived there already, so I don't know when he moved in, actually.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In his very early years, there was another house in the inner city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when-- I really don't know when [LAUGHS] he moved in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I left before him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But little by little, the house was taken over, I guess, with more of the Party dignitaries or whatever else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when-- when [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Chamberlain came, when they-- to sign what they thought was then 'peace in our time,' they all came in-- in the motorcade.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they signed it because there was-- in the Party headquarters, which was in Munich in another location.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the motorcade came to his private home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw the motorcade.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was on my way home from school on the bicycle, so I saw the motorcade go by.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, you couldn't see anybody who was in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
